\v 21 Bawo p…ôcuy pendeb…õk, mp…õ p…õntat…Ēyi k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ doru doncop m…Ē haŇč nd…õk…ôl, fum o fum af…Ēs…Ēt…Ēr…ôs p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 22 Mba Kanu p…ônat…Ēbel…ôr mataka mam…Ēk…Ē-…õ, k'ali fum …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēfis. Mba …õnabel…ôr mataka mam…Ēk…Ē teta ak…Ē …õnay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.  
\v 23 Awa, k…Ē w…ôl…Ēma oloku nu: ‚ÄĻM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl: Krist eyi nn…Ē,‚Äļ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, ‚ÄĻEyi nde-…õ,‚Äļ ta n…ôlaŇč w…ôkayi.  
\v 24 Bawo abaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ Krist k…Ē sayib…õ sa yem Ňčandewur doru, Ňčacy…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē mes mocuca, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčactam-…õ, Ňčatal…ôr ak…Ē Kanu k…ônay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.  
\v 25 N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl! Iloku nu mes mam…õ ta m…õntab…ôp-…õ. 
