\s1 K…ôder ka Wan ka W…ôrkun 
\r Mark 13.24-27; Luk 21.25-28 
\p  
\v 29 K…Ē Yesu endeŇč…ôr s…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē pucuy pa mata mam…Ēk…Ē pencep…ôr-…õ, gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē b…Ē p…ôndey…Ē gb…ôr…ôp, Ňčof Ňč…Ēf…Ēdes…Ēmar, c…Ēs c…ôndet…õmp…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm, f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…Ēm f…ôndeyikc…õ.\x - \xo 24:29 \xt Esayi 13.10; 34.4\x* 
\v 30 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta k…ôder ka Wan ka W…ôrkun tendewur d…ôk…Ēm, afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp Ňčandekul…õ-kul…õ k…ônes…õ disr…õ, Ňčacn…ôŇčk Wan ka W…ôrkun p…ôcder k…ôp k…ôroŇč d…ôf…ôn…Ēnt…ôr k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 31 T…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta k…ôfula luk p…ôp…ĒŇč it…Ē Wan ka W…ôrkun endesom m…õl…õk…õ …Ēn, m…Ēk…Ē moloŇčka afum aŇč…õ …õy…õk-y…õk moŇčkubut maŇčk…ôl…õ ma d…ôK…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 T…õt…ôk…ôs ta totubc…õn…õ ta k…ôt…Ēk ka fik 
\r Mark 13.28-31; Luk 21.29-33 
\p  
\v 32 K…Ē Yesu endeŇč…ôr s…Ē: ¬ęN…ôt…ôk…ôs totubc…õn…õ nt…õ k…ôt…Ēk ka fik k…ôment…ôr m…Ē: K…Ē wara wa ki w…õcaŇčk w…õl…õŇčk-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ a k…ôt…ôn k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.  
