\s1 Kanu gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôc…ôr…õ t…õm nt…õ doru dendelip m…Ē 
\r Mark 13.32-37; Luk 17.26-30,34-36 
\p  
\v 36 K…Ē Yesu oloku s…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta d…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē t…õm nt…õ doru dendelip m…Ē, ali fum …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ ti, ali m…õl…õk…õ k…Ē Wan Ňča s…Ē Ňčanc…ôr…õ f…õ ti, m…õn…õ Papa sona gboŇč.  
\v 37 T…Ēk…Ē t…õnayi t…õm ta Nuha m…Ē, it…Ē teta k…ôder ka Wan ka W…ôrkun k…ôndeyi.  
