\v 39 ali k…ôc…õmc…õmn…õ k…ôf…õt k…ônayi f…õ Ňča haŇč k…Ē kutup k…ônder k…Ē k…ôm…ôl…ôk Ňča f…ôp. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē k…ôder ka Wan ka W…ôrkun k…ôndeyi.  
\v 40 Awa, k…Ē arkun m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayi dal…õ-…õ, pal…õk w…ôkin, pasak w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 41 K'aran m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayi k…ôbif…ôli m…õŇčgb…õn-…õ, pal…õk w…ôkin, pasak w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 42 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, n…ôckar k…ôder k…Ēn t…õm f…ôp, bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Mariki monu mendeder m…Ē.  
\v 43 N…ôc…ôr…õ ti belbel k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka k…ôl…Ē p…ôc…ôr…õ t…õm ta pibi nt…õ w…ôke endeder d…ôŇčkiy…õ m…Ē, w…ôka k…ôl…Ē …Ēf…Ēdir…õ p…ôcbum kumba k…Ēn ta w…ôke p…ôb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 44 Ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ n…ôna s…Ē k…ôc…ôm…õ n…ôckar, bawo Wan ka W…ôrkun endeder t…õm nt…õ n…ônt…Ēy…Ē k…Ē amera m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 W…ômar…ôs w…ôlompu k…Ē w…ôt…Ēlomp 
\r Luk 12.41-48 
\p  
\v 45 K…Ē Yesu endeŇč…ôr s…Ē: ¬ęW…ômar…ôs w…ôsekt…ôrn…õ mariki m…Ēn p…ôck…Ēt…õn…õ amera k…ôy…Ē p…ôt…Ēt w…ôre mariki m…Ēn …õnc…ômb…ôr k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôbum ka amar…ôs alp…ôs ak…Ē, p…ôcs…ĒŇč Ňča yeri t…õm nt…õ p…ômar m…Ē-…õ?  
