\v 47 Kance icloku nu: Mariki m…Ēn mendes…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka daka d…Ēn f…ôp.  
\v 48 Mba k…Ē w…ômar…ôs olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ‚ÄĻMariki mem …õntay…õf…õ f…õ k…ôder,‚Äļ  
\v 49 k'oncop k…ôsut anapa …Ēn amar…ôs, p…ôcdi yeri p…ôcmun k…Ē acis,  
\v 50 mariki ma w…ômar…ôs w…ôkak…Ē endeder d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē k…Ē amera m…Ē, dec nd…õ …Ēnt…Ēc…ôr…õ m…Ē,  
\v 51 p…ôb…õl…ôs w…ômar…ôs w…ôkak…Ē, p…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēr…ôs abaŇč…õn…õ k…ôlomp m…Ē. Dif…Ē k…ôbok k…ôndeyi k…Ē k…ôŇčaŇč…ôr…õn…õ sek. 
\c 25  
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta ayec…ôra w…ôco at…Ēc…ôr…õ arkun 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr nt…õ: ¬ęT…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, d…õb…õ da d…ôk…Ēm dendeyi p…ôm…Ē ayec…ôra w…ôco at…Ēc…ôr…õ arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanal…õk s…ôlamp k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôgbaŇčn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…ôcam…ôt k…ônayi Ňča dac…Ē aŇč…õ anatoŇčkulu m…Ē, k…ôcam…ôt k…ôyi Ňča dac…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes m…Ē.  
\v 3 Nt…õ atoŇčkulu Ňčancl…õk s…ôlamp s…ôŇčan m…Ē, Ňčanal…õk…õn…õ f…õ moro.  
\v 4 Mba ayec…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ ac…ôr…õ mes m…Ē, Ňčal…õk s…ôlamp s…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ s…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ moro d…ôt…Ēk…Ēb…Ē.  
\v 5 Nt…õ w…ôgbaŇčn…õ oncwon k…ôder m…Ē, k…Ē mere m…Ēy…Ē ayec…ôra k…Ē Ňčandir…õ.  
\v 6 C…õkc…õk c…ôndeb…ôp, k…Ē dim dowur: ‚ÄĻAwa w…ôgbaŇčn…õ ender, n…ôwur pade pafayn…õ k…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 7 K…Ē ayec…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčantim…õ k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôlomp…ôs s…ôlamp saŇčan.  
\v 8 K…Ē ayec…ôra atoŇčkulu Ňčaloku ac…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes: ‚ÄĻN…ôpoc…õ su moro monu, k…ônim…õ k…Ē s…ôlamp sosu s…ônd…õ!‚Äļ  
\v 9 Mba k…Ē ac…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes Ňčaloku: ‚ÄĻMoro mosu m…Ēf…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ su k…ômot…õn…õ k…Ē n…ôna. M…õn…õ n…ôk…Ē n…ôway nda ak…Ē Ňčancam…ôs moro m…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 10 Ayec…ôra atoŇčkulu Ňčawur k…ôk…Ēway moro, k…Ē w…ôgbaŇčn…õ ender kumunt k…ôŇčan dar…ôŇč, ayec…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dukul…Ē k…Ē w…ôgbaŇčn…õ, k'ancaŇč kumba.  
\v 11 Nt…õ p…ôwon pipic m…Ē, k…Ē ayec…ôra atoŇčkulu Ňčander k…Ē Ňčaloku: ‚ÄĻMariki, mariki, m…ôgbit…õ su!‚Äļ  
\v 12 Mba k…Ē mariki mm…õ moluks…õ Ňča: ‚ÄĻKance icloku nu: Inc…ôr…õ f…õ nu!‚Äļ  
\v 13 Ta n…ôp…ôl…ôr, bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ d…Ēs…Ēk, n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ s…Ē dec nd…õ indeder m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta amar…ôs maas 
\r Luk 19.11-27 
\p  
\v 14 ¬ęTowur…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ w…ôrkun …õŇčfaŇč k…ôk…Ē mar…ônt, p…ôwe acar …Ēn p…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča daka d…Ēn k…ôm…õŇčk.  
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …Ēs…ĒŇč k…õma kilo k…ôcam…ôt w…ôcar w…ôkin, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč kilo k…ôm…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē w…ôka maas kilo katin, nt…õ …Ēs…ĒŇč nw…õ o nw…õ t…Ēk…Ē …õntam m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē mar…ônt.  
\v 16 W…ôcar nw…õ anas…ĒŇč k…ôm…õŇčk k…õma kilo k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē, …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôckaf…ôli-kaf…ôli waca haŇč k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē k…õma kilo k…ôcam…ôt k…ôdeŇč…ôrn…õ.  
\v 17 Nw…õ anas…ĒŇč k…õma kilo k…ôm…õr…ôŇč k…ôm…õŇčk m…Ē, nk…Ēn s…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôckaf…ôli-kaf…ôli waca haŇč k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…õma k…ôdeŇč…ôrn…õ kilo m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 18 W…ôcar nw…õ anas…ĒŇč k…õma kilo kin k…ôm…õŇčk m…Ē, …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôkay abi k'…õm…õŇčk p…ôsam pa mariki m…Ēn. 
\p  
\v 19 Nt…õ p…ôwon m…Ē, k…Ē mariki maŇčan mender, k'ewe acar aŇč…õ k…ôdeyif Ňča nt…õ Ňčamb…ôc m…Ē.  
\v 20 W…ôcar w…ôk…Ē anas…ĒŇč k…õma kilo k…ôcam…ôt k…ôm…õŇčk m…Ē, ender p…ôloku mariki m…Ēn: ‚ÄĻMariki, m…ônas…ĒŇč im k…ôm…õŇčk k…õma kilo k…ôcam…ôt, iŇčkaf…ôli-kaf…ôli waca k'is…Ēt…Ē s…Ē kilo k…ôcam…ôt k…ôdeŇč…ôr.‚Äļ  
\v 21 K…Ē mariki m…Ēn moloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻTentes…õ, w…ôcar w…ôt…Ēt m…ôy…Ēn…õ nw…õ p…ômar palaŇč m…Ē! M…ôlas k…ôlaŇč teta tes t…õf…õt, awa d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…ĒŇč d'indes…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr. P…ôb…Ēt …ôm k…Ē mariki mam.‚Äļ  
\v 22 W…ôcar nw…õ anas…ĒŇč k…õma kilo m…õr…ôŇč k…ôm…õŇčk m…Ē, ender p…ôloku: ‚ÄĻMariki, m…ônas…ĒŇč im k…ôm…õŇčk k…õma kilo m…õr…ôŇč, nt…õ iŇčkaf…ôli-kaf…ôli waca m…Ē, k'is…Ēt…Ē kilo m…õr…ôŇč k…ôdeŇč…ôr ka ki.‚Äļ  
\v 23 K…Ē mariki m…Ēn moloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻTentes…õ, w…ôcar w…ôt…Ēt m…ôy…Ēn…õ nw…õ p…ômar palaŇč m…Ē! M…ôlas k…ôlaŇč teta tes t…õf…õt, awa d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…ĒŇč d'indes…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr. P…ôb…Ēt …ôm k…Ē mariki mam.‚Äļ  
\v 24 W…ôcar w…ôk…Ē anas…ĒŇč k…ôm…õŇčk k…õma kilo kin m…Ē ender p…ôloku: ‚ÄĻMariki, inc…ôr…õ a fum w…ôcuca m…ôy…Ēn…õ: K…ôfo k…Ē m…ônt…õl nk…õ m…ônat…Ēgbal defet m…Ē, m…ôcpim yokom ny…õ m…ônat…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 25 Inanes…õ, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôk…Ēm…ôt k…õma kam d…ônt…Ēf: Ik…Ē nk…õ, m…ôbaŇč daka d…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ēn…õ dam m…Ē.  
\v 26 K…Ē mariki m…Ēn moloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻW…ôcar w…ôl…õc, w…ôfan! M…ôna m…ônac…ôr…õ a int…õl nde int…Ēgbal defet m…Ē, icpim yokom ny…õ int…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē?  
\v 27 P…ônamar m…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôsam pem am…õŇčk p…ôsam, k…Ē nt…õ ilukus m…Ē, k'imbaŇč p…ôsam pem is…Ēt…Ē s…Ē pi k…ôroŇč k…ôntaŇčgb…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 28 K…Ē mariki mm…õ moloku: ‚ÄĻN…ôbaŇč…ôr k…Ē k…õma, n…ôs…ĒŇč ki w…ôk…Ē …Ēs…Ēt…Ēn'em k…õma kilo w…ôco m…Ē.  
\v 29 Bawo, andeb…õr…õn…õ w…ôk…Ē …Ēy…Ē m…Ē haŇč p…ôlar k…Ē, mba w…ôt…Ēy…Ē, andebaŇč…ôr k…Ē ali p…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 30 N…ôb…õl…ôs w…ôcar w…ôt…Ēy…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…ôkubump ka nde dabaŇčka. Dif…Ē k…ôbok k…Ē k…ôŇčaŇč…ôr…õn…õ sek k…ôŇčk…Ēyi.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôgb…õy ka alompu k…Ē al…õc t…õm nt…õ doru dendelip m…Ē 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Yesu endeŇč…ôr s…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē Wan ka W…ôrkun endeder n…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn disr…õ k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ f…ôp-…õ, p…ônd…õ d…Ēc…Ēm d…Ēn da d…õb…õ.  
\v 32 AndeloŇčka afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč. P…ôgb…õy aŇč…õ k…Ē ak…Ē p…ôm…Ē nt…õ w…ôk…õk …õŇčgb…õy Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir m…Ē:  
\v 33 P…ôc…ômb…ôr alompu k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē al…õc k…ôca k…ômeriya p…ôm…Ē nt…õ w…ôk…õk …õnc…ômb…ôr Ňčkesiya k…ôca k…Ēn k…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē cir k…ôca k…Ēn k…ômeriya m…Ē.  
\v 34 Awa, w…ôb…õ p…ôloku ak…Ē Ňčayi k…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt m…Ē: ‚ÄĻN…ôder n…ôna aŇč…õ Papa kem ompoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē. N…ôl…õk k…õ, d…õb…õ nd…õ anac…ômb…ôr…õ nu k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ doru d…õnacop m…Ē.  
\v 35 Bawo dor d…õnasump…ôr im k…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇč im yeri, k…Ē amera Ňčowos im k…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇč im domun, k'iy…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra k…Ē n…ômbaŇč im,  
\v 36 inawur dis fos k…ôfe k…ôct…Ēr…ôs im k…Ē n…ômb…õr im yamos, k'incu k…Ē n…ôt…õn'em ac…Ēl, k'iyi d…ôbili k…Ē n…ônder n…ôn…ôŇčk im.‚Äļ  
\v 37 Awa, alompu Ňčaluks…õ k…Ē k…ôyif: ‚ÄĻMariki, ake t…õm t…Ē s…ônan…ôŇčk …ôm dor dosump…ôr …ôm, k…Ē s…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm yeri-…õ? Ake t…õm t…Ē amera Ňč…õnawos …ôm, k…Ē s…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm domun-…õ?  
\v 38 Ake t…õm t…Ē s…ônan…ôŇčk …ôm m…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra, k…Ē s…ômbaŇč …ôm-…õ? Ake t…õm t…Ē m…ônayi dis fos k…Ē s…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm yamos-…õ?  
\v 39 Ake t…õm t…Ē s…ônan…ôŇčk …ôm m…ôccu k…Ē s…ônt…õn'am ac…Ēl-…õ? Ake t…õm t…Ē m…ônayi d…ôbili, k…Ē s…ônder k…ôden…ôŇčk …ôm-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 40 K…Ē w…ôb…õ oloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻKance icloku nu: T…õm o t…õm t…Ē n…ôy…Ē tes tin ta mes m…Ēt…Ēt mam…Ēk…Ē nw…õ …õf…õt…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ aw…õnc im aŇča f…ôp dac…Ē m…Ē, ina yati n…ôy…Ē ti.‚Äļ 
\p  
\v 41 K…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē telip-…õ, w…ôb…õ p…ôdeloku ak…Ē Ňčayi k…Ē k…ôca k…ômeriya m…Ē: ‚ÄĻN…ôb…Ēl'em day, n…ôna aŇč…õ Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc m…Ē. N…ôk…Ē n…ôb…õr…õ d…ôn…õnc nd…õ d…Ēnt…Ēnim…õ doru o doru m…Ē, nd…õ analomps…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňä…õl…õc k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma Ňči m…Ē.  
\v 42 Bawo dor d…õnay'em k…Ē n…ônt…Ēs…ĒŇč im yeri, k…Ē amera Ňčowos im k…Ē n…ônt…Ēs…ĒŇč im domun.  
\v 43 Inayi decik…ôra k…Ē n…ônt…ĒbaŇč im, inawur dis fos k…ôfe k…ôct…Ēr…ôs im, k…Ē n…ônt…Ēs…ĒŇč im yamos, inacu k'iyi d…ôbili k…Ē n…ônt…Ēk…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk im.‚Äļ  
\v 44 Ňäa s…Ē Ňčayif: ‚ÄĻMariki, ake t…õm t…Ē s…ônan…ôŇčk …ôm dor d…Ēy'…ôm, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti amera Ňčowos …ôm, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti m…ôyi decik…ôra, m…ôyi dis fos, m…ôyi ta m…ôntamn…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti m…ôyi d…ôbili ta s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ômar …ôm-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 45 W…ôb…õ p…ôluks…õ Ňča: ‚ÄĻKance icloku nu: Nt…õ n…ônat…Ēy…Ēn…õ ti w…ôkin ak…Ē Ňčaf…õt…õ m…Ē dac…Ē, ina n…ônt…Ēy…Ēn…õ ti.‚Äļ  
\v 46 Akak…Ē Ňčandeb…õr…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs disr…õ ka Kanu nk…õ k…ônt…Ēlip doru o doru m…Ē, mba alompu Ňčandeb…õr…õ k…ôyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru.¬Ľ 
\c 26  
\s1 Ab…õ Ňčasek…õ Yesu t…õŇčk…ônd…ôm 
\r Mark 14.1-2; Luk 22.1-2 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu elip k…ôloku moloku mam…õ m…Ē, k'oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč:  
\v 2 ¬ęN…ônc…ôr…õ a k…Ē mata m…õr…ôŇč mendecep…ôr-…õ, k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif k…ôŇčyi. Andeb…õr Wan ka W…ôrkun afum d…ôwaca nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ŇčacaŇč k…Ē t…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl k…ôroŇč m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 3 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki aSuyif Ňčandek…ĒloŇčkan…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč nw…õ aŇčwe Kayif m…Ē,  
\v 4 Ňčat…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsump…ôr Yesu c…ôp…ônp…ôn disr…õ Ňčadif k…Ē.  
\v 5 Ti disr…õ k…Ē Ňčalok…õn…õ: ¬ęTa pasump…ôr k…Ē k…ôsata disr…õ ta tedes…ĒŇč…õ pidikc…õ pedeyi afum dac…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 W…ôran w…ôl…Ēma oloŇč…ôr domp da Yesu labund…õ 
\r Mark 14.3-9; Luk 7.36-50; IsaŇč 12.1-8 
\p  
\v 6 Nt…õ Yesu …õnayi Betani ndena Sim…ĒŇč w…ôcun…õ sen,  
\v 7 k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu. W…ôran nw…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr t…Ēk…Ēb…Ē pa alabat…ôr \f + \fr 26:7 \fq T…Ēk…Ēb…Ē pa alabat…ôr\ft  = T…Ēk…Ēb…Ē p…Ē mp…õ anclomps…õ tasar pefer p…õpat m…Ē. Tasar p…Ēt…Ēt pap…Ēk…Ē p'aŇčwe ¬ęalabat…ôr¬Ľ.\f* p…õlar…õ labund…õ da nar t…õp nd…õ deyeŇčk k…ôway m…Ē, Yesu p…ôyi d…õm…õsa k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ ender p…ôloŇč…ôr k…Ē labund…õ nd…õ f…ôp d…ôromp.  
\v 8 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč al…Ēma, k…Ē Ňčayifn…õ: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ …õl…ôs…ôr…õ-l…ôs…ôr…õ labund…õ dand…õ-…õ?  
\v 9 Anatam di k…ôcam…ôs k…ôway k…ôyeŇčki, pas…ĒŇč p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē at…Ēy…Ē daka.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 10 Mba k…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęN…ôce k…Ē! Ta ake t…Ē n…ôŇčnal…õ k…Ē-…õ? T…Ēy…Ē t…Ēt…Ēt t'…Ēy…Ē nn…Ē ina iyi m…Ē.  
\v 11 At…Ēy…Ē daka, Ňčayi nu dac…Ē t…õm f…ôp. Mba ina, n…ôf…Ēdey'em t…õm f…ôp.  
\v 12 Nt…õ oloŇč…ôr im labund…õ dand…õ d…ôris m…Ē, k…ôbel kem k'eyi k…ôlomp…ôs a pacwup ki.  
\v 13 Kance icloku nu: Nn…Ē o nn…Ē anded…ôŇčk Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt kaŇčk…õ doru dand…õ k…Ērk…Ēr m…Ē, aŇčloku s…Ē t…Ēy…Ē t…Ēt…Ēt nt…õ w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ē m…Ē k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka doru.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yudas …õfaŇč k…ôb…õr Yesu ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč d…ôwaca 
\r Mark 14.10-11; Luk 22.3-6 
\p  
\v 14 W…ôkin ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē, nw…õ ancwe Yudas w…ôka dare da Keriyot, …ĒŇčk…Ē nde ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ Ňčayi m…Ē,  
\v 15 k…ôk…Ēyif Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ il…õk Yesu ib…õr nu d…ôwaca-…õ, p…ôsam c…ôke p…Ē n…ôndes…ĒŇč im-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčal…Ēm gbeti gb…ôleŇč w…ôco maas (30), k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē Yudas …õy…õf…õ oŇč k…ôt…õn t…Ēy…Ē nt…õ endeb…õr…õ Yesu ab…õ akak…Ē d…ôwaca m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…ôboc k…ôsata 
\r Mark 14.12-21; Luk 22.7-14,21-23; IsaŇč 13.21-30 
\p  
\v 17 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da k…ôsata ka C…ôcom C…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl Lebin, ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęDeke m…ôfaŇč s…ôk…Ēlomps'am yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôb…õr…õ dare ndena fum w…ôl…Ēma, n…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻW…ôt…ôks…õ kosu oloku: T…õm tem t…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ, nn…Ē ndaram indecep…ôr…õn…õ k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif k…Ē ac…õps…õ em dar…ôŇč.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnasom Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs yeri ya k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē. 
\p  
\v 20 Nt…õ d…Ēf…Ēy d…õmb…ôp m…Ē,Yesu Ňčand…õ d…õm…õsa k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 21 Ňäayi k…ôdi yeri, k…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęKance icloku nu: W…ôkin nu dac…Ē, endeb…õr im ater…õn…õ em d…ôwaca.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē dis d…õnd…õnc…õ Ňča k…Ē Ňčam…Ēncn…õ, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt Yesu: ¬ęMariki, in'…Ēf…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē Yesu oloku: Nw…õ s…ômb…õr waca dap din disr…õ k…ôdi yeri m…Ē endeb…õr im ater…õn…õ em d…ôwaca.  
\v 24 Wan ka W…ôrkun endefi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic ti m…Ē. Mba p…ôl…õc pere peyi w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ endeb…õr Wan ka W…ôrkun ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē! K…ônat…Ēkom ka w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ k…ônatam k…ôtes…õ k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 25 Yudas nw…õ …õnayi k…ôy…Ē Yesu c…ôp…ônp…ôn m…Ē, eyif Yesu: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, in'…Ēf…Ē ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'oloku ti.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč ŇčampaŇčn…õ k…ôdi yeri t…õlp…ôs 
\r Mark 14.22-25; Luk 22.15-20; 1Ko 11.23-26 
\p  
\v 26 Nt…õ Ňčancdi yeri m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu …õl…õk k…ôcom, k'eyif Kanu barka, k'entepi ki k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…ôs ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ôbaŇč n…ôs…Ēm k…ôcom kaŇčk…õ, dis dem d…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 27 K'…õl…õk s…Ē t…Ēmb…ôl ta w…õn, nt…õ elip k…ôyif Kanu barka m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ômun w…õn waw…õ f…ôp,  
\v 28 mecir mem m…Ē, mm…õ aloŇč…õ k…ôcaŇč…ôs ka danapa da Kanu k…Ē k…ônay ka afum teta k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ka kiciya m…Ē.  
\v 29 Kance icloku nu: If…Ēs…Ēmun w…õn haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ indegb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ômun wi k…Ē n…ôna, nde d…õb…õ da Papa kem m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 30 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôleŇč…ôs meleŇč mokor-kor…õ Kanu m…Ē, Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčawurn…õ ntende k…ôca ka t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif. 
\s1 Yesu oloku Piy…õr a endegb…õk…ôl k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ēn 
\r Mark 14.26-31; Luk 22.31-34; IsaŇč 13.37-38 
\p  
\v 31 Nt…õ Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčamb…ôp t…Ēr…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna akaŇč…õ f…ôp n…ôndelukus im dar…ôŇč, bawo Yecic…ôs Yosoku yoloku: ‚ÄĻIndesut w…ôk…õk, Ňčkesiya y…Ēc…Ēl y…õsams…ôr.‚Äļ\x - \xo 26:31 \xq \xt ¬ęIndesut w…ôk…õk, Ňčkesiya ya y…Ēc…Ēl y…õsams…ôr.¬Ľ \xt Sakary 13.7\x* 
\v 32 Mba k'indef…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē-…õ, indek…Ēkar nu Kalile.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAli f…ôp f…ôlukus …ôm dar…ôŇč, ina if…Ēlukus …ôm dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 34 K…Ē Yesu oloku Piy…õr: ¬ęKance, iclok'…ôm, pibi pamp…õ yati, m…ôndegb…õk…ôl k…ôc…ôr'em k…ômaas a kicipi k…ôccam.¬Ľ  
\v 35 Mba Piy…õr p…ôcgb…õk…ôl ti: ¬ęAli s…ôcfi k…Ē m…ôna, if…Ēgb…õk…ôl a inc…ôr'am.¬Ľ Ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč ak…Ē f…ôp toloku tin tayi t…Ē Ňčancloku. 
\s1 Yesu ontola Kanu nde Ketsemane 
\r Mark 14.32-42; Luk 22.40-46 
\p  
\v 36 Ti disr…õ k…Ē Yesu ender k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč nde k…ôfo nk…õ aŇčwe Ketsemane\f + \fr 26:36 \fq Ketsemane\ft  it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē c…ôArame ¬ęD…ôk…ôf…Ēc…ôs moro¬Ľ. \f* m…Ē, k'oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč: ¬ęN…ônd…õ nn…Ē, ib…Ēl…õ nu pipic itola Kanu.¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk…õn…õ Piy…õr k…Ē awut a Sebede m…õr…ôŇč, nt…õ dis d…õnd…õnc…õ Yesu k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ k…Ē m…Ē,  
\v 38 k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAb…ôk…ôc Ňč…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôd…õnc'em p…ôm…Ē ifi. N…ôyi nn…Ē, ta padir…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 39 K…Ē Yesu …Ēmb…Ēl…õn…õ Ňča pipic, k'ontotn…õ k'…õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôc…ôp tobu d…ônt…Ēf, k'ontola nt…õ: ¬ęPapa kem, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…ôwos…õ ti-…õ, m…ôb…Ēl…õn'em t…Ēmb…ôl pa k…ôt…Ēr…ôs pamp…õ! Mba baf…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ifaŇč ti m…Ē, mba t…Ēk…Ē m…ôna Papa m…ôfaŇč ti m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 40 K…Ē Yesu ender p…ôb…ôp ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčacdir…õ. K'eyif Piy…õr: ¬ęN…ôntam f…õ k…ôt…Ēdir…õ k…Ē ina ali dec din ba?  
\v 41 Ta n…ôdir…õ, n…ôtola Kanu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ômb…õr…õ k…ôwak…ôs nk…õ k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôy…Ē mes m…õl…õc m…Ē. P…ômbas mera yonu k…ôy…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, mba n…ôy…Ē f…õ s…Ēk…ôt k…ôy…Ē ti.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 42 K…Ē Yesu …Ēmb…Ēl…õ s…Ē ta m…õr…ôŇč k'ontola Kanu nt…õ: ¬ęPapa kem, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a t…Ēmb…ôl pamp…õ p…Ēf…Ēb…Ēl…õ ta imun pi-…õ, awa, t…õfaŇč tam teyi!¬Ľ  
\v 43 K…Ē Yesu olukus, k'ender p…ôb…ôp ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčacd…ĒŇč…ôs, nt…õ f…Ēr y…õnal…Ēl Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 44 K…Ē Yesu …õsak Ňča k'…Ēmb…Ēl…õ s…Ē, k'ontola s…Ē Kanu ta maas, p…ôcgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē moloku min mayi.  
\v 45 K…Ē Yesu oluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčayi m…Ē, k'…õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňča: ¬ęN…ôndir…õ s…Ē, k…ôŇčes…ôm k…Ē n…ônd…õ! N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl: T…õm t…õmb…ôp, amb…õr Wan ka W…ôrkun aciya d…ôwaca!  
\v 46 N…ôy…õf…õ, paŇčk…Ēn! Bawo nw…õ eyi k…ôb…õr im afum d…ôwaca m…Ē, …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôsump…ôr ka Yesu 
\r Mark 14.43-50; Luk 22.47-53; IsaŇč 18.2-11 
\p  
\v 47 Yesu p…ôs…Ēr…Ēlok-loku, gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Yudas nw…õ …õnayi ac…õps…õ a Yesu aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē, ender p…ôsol…õ k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr-t…Ēmp…ôr sakma k…Ē t…Ēk yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē. AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki aSuyif Ňčanasom Ňča.  
\v 48 Yudas nw…õ …õncb…õr Yesu ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē, …õnas…ĒŇč as…Ēdar t…õm…ônc…õ nt…õ: ¬ęNw…õ iŇčk…Ēcup m…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēf…Ē w…ôkak…Ē. N…ôsump…ôr k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 49 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Yudas ender, k'…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu, k'ewe k…Ē: ¬ęIyif …ôm, W…ôt…ôks…õ,¬Ľ k'oncup k…Ē.  
\v 50 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęWanapa, nt…õ m…ônder k…ôy…Ē m…Ē, m…ôy…Ē ti.¬Ľ K…Ē afum akak…Ē Ňčanc…ĒŇčn…õ k…Ē Ňčant…ôps…ôr Yesu waca, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē.  
\v 51 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…ôkin asol a Yesu dac…Ē, owur…õ dakma k'…õnc…õp w…ôcar ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, k'eŇčgbinti Ňči.  
\v 52 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôluks…õ dakma dam dobom, bawo nw…õ o nw…õ endey…õf…ôr…õn…õ dakma m…Ē, dakma dendedif k…Ē.  
\v 53 M…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a if…Ētam k…ôwe Papa kem nw…õ …õntam k…ôk…õr'em m…õl…õk…õ as…Ēdar alar…ôm c…ôgba w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ca wul k…Ē wul ba?  
\v 54 C…ôke c…Ē Yecic…ôs Yosoku y…õntam k…ôlar…õ-…õ? Bawo y…õnaloku a tant…õ t…Ē p…ômar mes mam…õ medecep…ôr?¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 55 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē b…Ē Yesu …õnaloku k…ônay kaŇčk…Ē: ¬ęN…ôwur k…ôdesump…ôr im, n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr-t…Ēmp…ôr sakma k…Ē t…Ēk yosutn…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ iŇčy…Ēn…õ kalbante m…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk inder ind…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu ict…ôks…õ ta n…ônder n…ôsump…ôr im-…õ.  
\v 56 Mba mam…õ f…ôp meyi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Yecic…ôs ya sayib…õ y…õlar…õ m…Ē. K…Ē ac…õps…õ dar…ôŇč Ňčasak Yesu k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ. 
\s1 Yesu eyi nda aboc kiti 
\r Mark 14.53-65; Luk 22.54-55,63-71; IsaŇč 18.12-24 
\p  
\v 57 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanasump…ôr Yesu m…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē ndena w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč Kayif, d…ôndo at…ôks…õ sariy…õ k…Ē abeki aSuyif Ňčanab…ôps…õn…õ.  
\v 58 Piy…õr …õnac…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč p…ôb…Ēl…õ haŇč nde abaŇčka Ňča k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč. K…Ē Piy…õr …õmb…õr…õ d…ôsaŇčka k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ k'abum a k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôloŇčn…õ Kayif k…ôs…ôk p…ôck…Ēkc…õ nt…õ mes ma Yesu mendek…Ēlip m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 59 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k'aboc kiti aSuyif f…ôp Ňčanct…õn yem ny…õ Ňčantam k…ôyems…õn…õ Yesu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ padif k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 60 Mba Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ, ali nt…õ sede alar…ôm Ňčanader Ňčabonc…õ k…Ē yem m…Ē. T…õlp…ôs k…Ē sede m…õr…ôŇč s…ônder,  
\v 61 ns…õ s…ônaloku: ¬ęYesu oloku: ‚ÄĻIntam k…ôcek…ôli k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, ic…ômb…ôr s…Ē ki mata maas disr…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 62 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õy…õf…õ k'eyif Yesu: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēluks…õ su t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm ba? C…ôke c…Ē m…ôŇčloku teta moloku ma sede mm…õ akaŇč…õ Ňčambonc am m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 63 Mba k…Ē Yesu …õncaŇčk. K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTewe ta Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi m…Ē, m…ôloku su k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist, Wan ka Kanu-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 64 K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn‚Äôoloku ti. Mba icloku nu, k…ôy…õf…õ oŇč nd…õk…ôl, n…ônden…ôŇčk Wan ka W…ôrkun p…ônd…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes f…ôp m…Ē, p…ôcder n…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn disr…õ k…ôp ka d…ôK…Ēm k…ôroŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 65 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õwal-wali yamos y…Ēn p…ôcloku: ¬ę∆Ül…Ēm…ôs Kanu! Sede s…ôre s…Ē p…ômar payif-…õ? N…ône t…Ēk…Ē ontubc…õn…õn…õ Kanu m…Ē, k…ôl…Ēm…ôs ka Kanu k…Ē.  
\v 66 C…ôke c…Ē n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ moloku: ¬ęM…õn…õ padif k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 67 Ti disr…õ k…Ē Ňčayuk…ôr Yesu lin d…ôk…ôro, k…Ē Ňčantim…ôs k…Ē Ňčkulma, al…Ēma Ňčacsut k…Ē waca d…ôkanca, Ňčacloku:  
\v 68 ¬ęKrist w…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu, m…ôbonc…ôr su ma, nw…õ osut …ôm m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Piy…õr …õŇčgb…õk…ôl k…ôc…ôr…õ ka Yesu 
\r Mark 14.66-72; Luk 22.56-62; IsaŇč 18.17,25-27 
\p  
\v 69 Piy…õr p…ônd…õ nde dabaŇčka, k…Ē w…ôcar w…ôyec…ôra w…ôl…Ēma …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôna w…ôkak…Ē m…ônd…õ m…Ē, n…ôn'…õnayi k…Ē Yesu w…ôka Kalile.¬Ľ  
\v 70 Mba k…Ē Piy…õr …õŇčgb…õk…ôl ti afum f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôcloku: ¬ęIna, inc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ m…ôna m…ôfaŇč k…ôloku m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 71 Nt…õ nk…Ēn Piy…õr …Ēnck…Ē d…ôkusuŇčka k…ôwur m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē s…Ē, k'oloku afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi d…ônda m…Ē: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ, Ňča Ňčanayi k…Ē Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt.¬Ľ  
\v 72 K…Ē Piy…õr …õŇčgb…õk…ôl s…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē k'…õnd…õr…ôm: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ f…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 73 P…ôwon f…õ ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ di m…Ē Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Piy…õr k…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôna s…Ē afum akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē n…ôyi, tolok-loku tam tement…ôr ti.¬Ľ  
\v 74 K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm: ¬ęKanu k…ôt…Ēr…ôs im k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôyem…õ k'ind…õ-…õ! Inc…ôr…õ f…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ n…ôŇčle m…Ē!¬Ľ Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē kicipi k…ôncam.  
\v 75 K…Ē Piy…õr …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ moloku m…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęM…ôndegb…õk…ôl k…ôt…Ēc…ôr'em k…ômaas a kicipi k…ôccam.¬Ľ K…Ē Piy…õr owur dabaŇčka k'ombok belbel. 
\c 27  
\s1 AŇčkek…ôr…õ Yesu ndena Pilat 
\r Mark 15.1; Luk 23.1-2; IsaŇč 18.28-32 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ b…ôtb…ôt b…õmb…ôp m…Ē, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki aSuyif f…ôp ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ a padif Yesu.  
\v 2 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôkot k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē Pilat d…ôwaca nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka s…ôdare sa Yude m…Ē. 
\s1 Defi da Yudas 
\r Asom 1.18-19 
\p  
\v 3 Nt…õ Yudas nw…õ …õnawur…õ Yesu p…ôb…õr k…Ē ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca …õn…ôŇčk a k…ôdif k'aŇčk…Ē Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē ab…Ēc Ňč…õmb…õr…õ k…Ē. K'oluks…õ gbeti gb…ôleŇč w…ôco maas aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki,  
\v 4 p…ôcloku: ¬ęInciya, imb…õr w…ôt…Ēciya nu d…ôwaca nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ padif k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ Mba aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki Ňčaloku: ¬ęYudas, tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēm…Ēm…ôn f…õ s…ôna! M…ôna tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēm…Ēm…ôn!  
\v 5 K…Ē Yudas …õŇčgbal p…ôsam d…ôndo k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôgb…õkn…õ k'efi.  
\v 6 K…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč ŇčaloŇčka gb…ôleŇč ba gbeti mb…õ, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęSariy…õ s…ôwos…õ f…õ su k…ôb…õr p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē k…õl…õ ka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, bawo k…ôway ka mecir k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 7 Nt…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk…õn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôway…õ ka gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē dal…õ da w…ôs…õl, p…ôy…Ēn…õ di d…ôk…ôwup da acik…ôra.  
\v 8 Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k'as…Ēr…Ēwe d…ôk…ôwup…õn…õ dad…Ēk…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē ¬ęDal…õ da Mecir.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ moloku mm…õ sayib…õ Yeremy …õnad…ôŇčk m…Ē, m…õlar…õ: ¬ęŇäanal…õk gbeti gb…ôleŇč w…ôco maas. Gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē b…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē,  
\v 10 k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ bi teta dal…õ da w…ôs…õl, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ Mariki …õnasom im ti m…Ē.¬Ľ\f + \fr 27:10 \xt Sakary 11.12-13\ft  k…Ē m…ôm…Ēm…ôn s…Ē \xt Yeremy 18.2-3; 19.1-2; 32.6-15\f* 
\s1 Yesu …õnc…ôm…õ f…Ēr kiriŇč ya Pilat k…ôkiti 
\r Mark 15.2-5; Luk 23.2-5,9-10; IsaŇč 18.29-38 
\p  
\v 11 K…Ē w…ôb…õ Pilat eyif Yesu: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'oloku ti.¬Ľ  
\v 12 Mba ali toloku tin Yesu …õnaloku f…õ k…ôluks…õ moloku ma k…ôyems…õn…õ mm…õ aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki Ňčanabonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 13 Ti disr…õ, k…Ē w…ôb…õ Pilat eyif k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęMes m…õl…õc m…õlar…ôm mm…õ Ňčambonc am m…Ē, m…ôf…Ēne mi ba?¬Ľ  
\v 14 Mba ali toloku tin Yesu …õnaluks…õ f…õ k…Ē, ti t…õnawos…ôs w…ôb…õ Pilat kusu p…ôp…ĒŇč. 
\s1 W…ôb…õ Pilat osom a padif Yesu 
\r Mark 15.6-14; Luk 23.13-23; IsaŇč 18.39-40 
\p  
\v 15 K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif, w…ôkiriŇč ka s…ôdare sa Yude …õncsak…õ afum y…õŇč…ôn k…ôren o k…ôren tataka ta k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ, fum w…ôkin ayi d…ôbili dac…Ē nw…õ k…ônay ka afum k…ôncfaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 16 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē w…ôyi d…ôbili w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi nw…õ tewe t…Ēn t…õnasam d…Ēt…Ēf m…Ē, pacwe k…Ē Yesu Barabas.  
\v 17 Nt…õ ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Pilat eyif Ňča: ¬ęYesu Barabas k…Ē Yesu nw…õ aŇčwe Krist m…Ē, an'…Ē n…ôfaŇč isak k…Ē y…õŇč…ôn-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 18 Pilat …õnac…ôr…õ a k…ôraca k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Ňčal…õk Yesu Ňčab…õr k…Ē d…ôwaca.  
\v 19 T…õm nt…õ Pilat …õnand…õ d…ôŇčkiti m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn osom pak…Ēloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm tey'…ôm dac…Ē k…Ē fum w…ôlompu w…ôkaw…õ! Bawo pibi pa m…Ēk…Ē int…Ēr…Ēna belbel icw…õr…ôp teta fum w…ôkaw…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki ŇčagbiŇč…ôr k…ônay ka afum k…ôloku a pasak…õ Ňča Barabas, padif Yesu.  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôb…õ Pilat eyif k…ônay: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč an'…Ē n…ôfaŇč a pasak…õ nu y…õŇč…ôn-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęBarabas!¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Pilat eyif Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęAk'indey…Ēn…õ oŇč Yesu nw…õ aŇčwe Krist m…Ē?¬Ľ K…Ē f…ôp f…ôloku: ¬ęM…ôcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl!¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē Pilat …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôyif Ňča: ¬ęP…ôl…õc pere p'…Ēy…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ Mba k…Ē k…ônay ka afum k…ônaŇčkan…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęM…ôcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl!¬Ľ  
\v 24 Nt…õ Pilat …õnac…ôr…õ a …Ēf…Ētam tes o tes, k…Ē pidikc…õ pa k…ônay ka afum p…õmb…õk k…ôb…õk d…ôm, k'…õl…õk domun k'embik…õn…õ waca f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč, k'oloku: ¬ęIsar…õ f…õ kiciya ka defi da fum w…ôkaw…õ. N…ôn'endesar…õ kiciya ka k…ôdif k…Ēn!¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčaloku: ¬ęS…ôwos…õ k…ôsar…õ teta defi d…Ēn, s…ôna k…Ē awut asu!¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē Pilat …õsak…õ afum aŇč…õ Barabas, k…Ē Barabas …ĒŇčk…Ē y…õŇč…ôn. Nt…õ Pilat elip k…ôsom pasut…õ Yesu t…Ēr…ĒŇčk…Ēn m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr k…Ē afum d…ôwaca a pacaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl. 
\s1 As…Ēdar Ňčafani Yesu 
\r Mark 15.16-20; Luk 23.11; IsaŇč 19.2-3 
\p  
\v 27 K'as…Ēdar a Pilat ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Yesu tedisr…õ ta k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē ŇčaloŇčka d…õŇčgb…õŇčk dad…Ēk…Ē f…ôp nd…õ d…õnak…õl k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 28 K'as…Ēdar Ňčawur…õ Yesu yamos y…Ēn k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē burumus beyim.  
\v 29 K…Ē Ňčandun…õ k…Ē aŇčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē Ňča b…õŇčk nŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôp k…Ē d…ôromp m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē k…ôgbo d…ôk…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ē k…ôŇčgbasar k'ab…õ, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôp…õ k…Ē suwu Ňčacfani k…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęIŇčyif …ôm, w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif!¬Ľ  
\v 30 K…Ē Ňčayuk…ôr Yesu lin k…Ē Ňčal…õk k…ôgbo Ňčacsut k…Ē d…ôromp.  
\v 31 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôfani Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawur…õ k…Ē burumus b…Ēk…Ē Ňčanab…õr k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē s…Ē yamos y…Ēn. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē k…ôk…ĒcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl. 
\s1 AncaŇč Yesu d…ôk…ôt…Ēk k…ôp…ômp…ôl 
\r Mark 15.21-32; Luk 23.26-43; IsaŇč 19.16-24 
\p  
\v 32 Nt…õ as…Ēdar Ňčancwur dare m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk w…ôrkun w…ôka dare da Sir…õn w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ancwe Sim…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr k…Ē y…õb…ôc ya k…ôgbaŇčn…õ t…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl ny…õ anak…Ē k…ôcaŇč Yesu m…Ē.  
\v 33 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp k…ôfo nk…õ aŇčwe Kolkota m…Ē, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęK…ôfo ka K…ômb…õmb…ôl…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 34 K'as…Ēdar Ňčas…ĒŇč Yesu w…õn w…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl p…ôdok…ôt, mba nt…õ …õnat…õm wi temer m…Ē, …õnawos…õ f…õ wi k…ômun.  
\v 35 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkot yampuŇčpuŇč teta k…ôyer yamos y…Ēn.\f + \fr 27:35 \ft M…ôm…Ēm…ôn \xt Yabura 22.18\f* 
\v 36 K…Ē Ňčand…õ Ňčacbum k…Ē.  
\v 37 K'ant…ôp k…Ē domp tak…ôroŇč yecic…ôs ny…õ y…õnaloku tes nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k'andif k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ Yesu …Ēf…Ē, w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif.¬Ľ  
\v 38 AnacaŇč s…Ē Yesu k…ôs…ôk d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl t…õm tin k…Ē calbante m…õr…ôŇč, w…ôkin p…ôyi k…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, w…ôk…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē k…ôca k…ômeriya. 
\p  
\v 39 Afum acep…ôr Ňčacl…Ēm…ôs k…Ē Ňčacf…õk k…Ē domp.  
\v 40 Ňäacloku: ¬ęM…ôna nw…õ m…ôncek…ôli k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, m…ôc…ômb…ôr s…Ē ki mata maas disr…õ m…Ē, m…ôyacn…õ m…ônas…ôrka! K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a Wan ka Kanu m…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ, m…ôtor oŇč d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl yay…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 41 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif k…Ē abeki s…Ē Ňčancfani Yesu Ňčacloku:  
\v 42 ¬ę∆źnayac al…Ēma, mba …Ēf…Ētam k…ôyacn…õ nk…Ēns…ôrka! W…ôb…õ ka Yisrayel …Ēy…Ēn…õ: Awa p…ôtor oŇč ma d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl yay…õ, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôgb…õk…ôr k…Ē k…ôlaŇč kosu!  
\v 43 ∆źŇčgb…õk…ôr Kanu amera, awa Kanu k…ôyac k…Ē oŇč ma, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu k…ômb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē. Bawo oloku: ‚ÄĻWan ka Kanu iy…Ēn…õ!‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 44 Calbante aŇč…õ anacaŇč k…Ē Yesu m…Ē Ňčacl…Ēm…ôs k…Ē tin tayi. 
\s1 Defi da Yesu 
\r Mark 15.33-41; Luk 23.44-49; IsaŇč 19.28-30 
\p  
\v 45 P…ôndeyi daŇč k…Ē kubump k…ôntor d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp haŇč salifana.  
\v 46 Salifana s…ôndeb…ôp, k…Ē Yesu oŇčkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ę\it Eloyi, Eloyi, lema sabaktani?\it*¬Ľ\x - \xo 27:46 \xq \xt Yesu …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ moloku ma Dawuda \xt Yabura 22.2\x* It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē: ¬ęKanu kem, Kanu kem, ta ake t…Ē m…ôsak'em-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 47 K…Ē afum al…Ēma ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē, Ňčanane k…Ē dim. Ňäancloku k…ôf…Ēt…Ē disr…õ a AŇčnabi Eli eyi k…ôwe.  
\v 48 K…Ē fum w…ôkin …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēl…õk yaŇčgba, ny…õ …õnapuk d…ôm…ônc…Ēnc…Ē m…Ē, k'…õn…õps…ôr yi d…ôk…ômota k'encenc k…Ē yi a p…ômun.  
\v 49 Mba k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęM…ôkar ma, pam…Ēm…ôn belbel k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Eli endeder k…ôdeyac k…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 50 K…Ē Yesu oŇčkul…õ s…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč, a k'oluks…õ Kanu af…Ēk…ôl Ňč…Ēn.  
\v 51 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē k…ôloto k…ôlel nk…õ k…ôŇčk…ôŇčk t…Ēks…Ē ta k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē k…ôŇčgb…õr…õ dac…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ tak…ôroŇč haŇč tant…Ēf. K…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õy…õf…õ k…ôyikc…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē masar m…õŇčgb…õr…õ,  
\v 52 k…Ē cufu c…ôŇčgbit…õ, k…Ē c…ôbel ca afum a Kanu alar…ôm Ňčaf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē.  
\v 53 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ d…ôcufu nt…õ Yesu …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ Yerusal…õm dare nd…õ ampus…õ Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ afum alar…ôm.  
\v 54 W…ôb…õ k'as…Ēdar w…ôRom k…Ē amar…õn…õ …Ēn as…Ēdar ak…Ē Ňčanayi di Ňčacbum k…ôbel ka Yesu m…Ē, Ňčanes…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč nt…õ Ňčanan…ôŇčk ant…Ēf k…ôyikc…õ, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…õnayi k…ôfi ka Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ, Wan ka Kanu yati …õnayi!¬Ľ  
\v 55 Aran alar…ôm Ňčanac…ôm…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õ Ňčacm…Ēm…ôn, aran aŇč…õ Ňčanasol k…Ē Yesu k…ôy…õf…õ Kalile k…ôdeb…ôc…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 56 Aran akak…Ē dac…Ē, Mari w…ôka Makdala, Mari iya w…ôka Sak k…Ē Isifu, k…Ē iya ka awut arkun a Sebede. 
\s1 Antor…õ Yesu d…ôkufu 
\r Mark 15.42-47; Luk 23.50-56; IsaŇč 19.38-42 
\p  
\v 57 Nt…õ d…Ēf…Ēy d…õmb…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôka daka w…ôl…Ēma ender, w…ôka dare da Arimate …õnayi, pacwe k…Ē Isifu. Nk…Ēn s…Ē w…ôc…õps…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi.  
\v 58 K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē ndena Pilat k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôtola k…Ē k…ôbel ka Yesu. K…Ē Pilat osom a pas…ĒŇč k…Ē ki.  
\v 59 K…Ē Isifu …õl…õk k…ôbel ka Yesu, k'…õn…õps…ôr ki kasaŇčke ka k…ôloto k…ôtel…ôr k…ôfu,  
\v 60 k'ontor…õ k…ôbel ka Yesu d…ôkufu nk…õ anat…Ētor…õ w…ôfi k…ôr…õsna m…Ē, kufu nk…õ nk…Ēn Isifu anay…Ēk ka nk…Ēns…ôrka d…ôtasar m…Ē, k'osunc…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da kufu kaŇčk…Ē tasar t…Ēp…ĒŇč, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē.  
\v 61 Awa, Mari w…ôka Makdala k…Ē Mari nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ iya ka Sak k…Ē Isifu m…Ē Ňčanayi di, Ňčand…õ Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ kufu. 
\s1 K…ôbum ka kufu 
\p  
\v 62 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da tataka tolomp…ôsn…õn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k'aFarisi Ňčasol k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ndena Pilat,  
\v 63 k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęMariki, s…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a w…ôyem…õ w…ôkaw…õ …õnaloku nt…õ …õnayi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē: ‚ÄĻTataka ta maas ta defi dem, indef…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 64 Awa, m…ôsom afum Ňčacbum kufu k…Ēn haŇč tataka ta maas, ta ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčadeder Ňčakiy…õ k…ôbel k…Ēn, Ňčakaf…ôl…õ k…ôloku afum: ‚ÄĻN…ôn…ôŇčk, …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē!‚Äļ Yem yay…Ēk…Ē yendeb…õk s…Ē yecep…ôr y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 65 K…Ē Pilat oloku Ňča: ¬ęIwos…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč nu as…Ēdar, n…ôy…Ē Ňča Ňčabum kufu kaŇčk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôfaŇč ti m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 66 Awa, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs tobum ta kufu nk…õ, k…Ē Ňčasunc…õ ki tasar p…Ēp…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr afum Ňčancbum ki. 
\c 28  
\s1 Yesu k…ôf…Ēt…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē 
\r Mark 16.1-10; Luk 24.1-12; IsaŇč 20.1-10 
\p  
\v 1 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm, sandeŇč b…ôtb…ôt, Mari w…ôka dare da Makdala k…Ē Mari w…ôl…Ēma Ňčander k…ôm…Ēm…ôn kufu.  
\v 2 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňčeyikc…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, bawo m…õl…õk…õ ma Mariki m…õnator d…ônt…Ēf k…ôdebiŇčk…ôli tasar, m…õnd…õ s…Ē pi k…ôroŇč.  
\v 3 M…õl…õk…õ mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnayi p…ôm…Ē p…ômot pa d…ôk…Ēm, yamos ya mi yefer…õ poŇč.  
\v 4 K…Ē as…Ēdar abum a kufu Ňčayikc…õn…õ k…ônes…õ, Ňčam…Ēmpn…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ŇčaŇčfi m…Ē.  
\v 5 Mba k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku aran: ¬ęTa n…ôna n…ônes…õ, bawo inc…ôr…õ a Yesu w…ôk…Ē anacaŇč d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl m…Ē, n…ôyi k…ôt…õn.  
\v 6 Eyi f…õ d…õ, …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku ti m…Ē. N…ôder n…ôm…Ēm…ôn nn…Ē k…ôfo nk…õ anaboc k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 7 N…ôkuf…õ n…ôk…Ēloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč a Yesu …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē, awa a n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp k…Ē Kalile, dif…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē. N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl: Tat…Ēk…Ē t'iy…Ēna toloku nu.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē aran aŇč…õ Ňčamb…Ēl…õ kufu nk…õ kat…ôna k…ônes…õ k…Ē p…ôbotu p…Ēp…ĒŇč disr…õ, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēloku ti ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč.  
\v 9 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Yesu ender aran aŇč…õ tekiriŇč k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęIyif nu!¬Ľ K…Ē aran aŇč…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē Ňčanc…ôp…õ k…Ē suwu k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē w…õc…ôk teta k…ôlel…ôs k…Ēn.  
\v 10 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ, n…ôk…Ē n…ôloku aw…õnc im aŇča a Ňčak…Ē Kalile, a dif…Ē Ňčandek…Ēn…ôŇčk im. 
\s1 Abum kufu Ňčal…Ēm…ôr ab…õ mes mm…õ m…õnacep…ôr nde d…ôkufu m…Ē 
\p  
\v 11 Nt…õ aran aŇč…õ Ňčanayi d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, awa k…Ē abum a d…ôkufu al…Ēma Ňčamb…õr…õ dare k…Ē Ňčal…Ēm…ôr aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 12 Nt…õ ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…Ē abeki m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč as…Ēdar akak…Ē p…ôsam p…õlar…ôm,  
\v 13 k…Ē Ňčasom as…Ēdar akak…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęN…ôde n…ôloku: ‚ÄĻAc…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčanderna Ňčakiy…õ k…Ē, t…õt…ôŇčn…õ s…ôdir…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 14 K…Ē w…ôkiriŇč ene ti-…õ, s…ôŇčk…Ēc…ôr…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr k…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta ant…Ēr…ôs nu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē as…Ēdar ŇčambaŇč p…ôsam k…Ē Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē analoku Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē taruku pa yem pap…Ēk…Ē p…õsam aSuyif dac…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu ement…ôrn…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč 
\r Mark 16.14-18; Luk 24.36-49; IsaŇč 20.19-23; Asom 1.6-8 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin ŇčaŇčk…Ē Kalile, nde t…Ēr…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnabonc…ôr Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 17 Nt…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ k…Ē, mba k…Ē al…Ēma Ňča dac…Ē Ňčanalip f…õ k…ôlaŇč tet…Ēn.  
\v 18 K…Ē Yesu …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Ňča, k'oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč im k…ôtam f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôK…Ēm haŇč d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 19 N…ôk…Ē, n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp k…ôy…Ēn…õ ac…õps…õ em dar…ôŇč, n…ôcgb…ôt Ňča d…ôromun tewe ta Kas, ta Wan k…Ē t'Amera Ňäecempi,  
\v 20 n…ôct…ôks…õ Ňča k…ôlel…ôs mosom m…Ēk…Ē isom nu m…Ē f…ôp. Awa k…Ē ina iyi nu dac…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk haŇč doru delip.¬Ľ